<lb>
<pdiv>
<p ln="[1]"><firstl>Carl Chessman interviews San Quentin P.T.A. before leaving on</firstl>
<lb>his . . . . . . . . annual tour of California Death U&hyphen;niversities.</p></pdiv>
<lb>
<pdiv>
<p ln="[2]">Caryl Chess&hyphen; Man is in sickly California writing death threats to
<lb>the Wizard of Oz, the green giant announces his trial will be held
<lb>in the stomach of . . . . . . . . Junipero Serra.</p></pdiv>
<lb>
<pdiv>
<p ln="[3]">Charlie Chaplin &amp; Sitting Bull walk hand in hand through the
<lb>World Series, Chest&hyphen; Mann steals all the bases except Home &amp;
