<lb>
<pdiv>
<p ln="[1]">ALL BOOM SHOOTING TO BE DONE FROM FAR OUT. . . . . . . .
<lb>CLOSEUPS TO BE SHOT ZOOMING IN . . . CAMERA PANS THE SET
<lb>ON THE WAY BACK OUT . . . . . .</p></pdiv>
<pb n="35">
<lb>
<pdiv>
<p ln="[2]">Film to be used in shooting reel one. BLACK OR WHITE OR
<lb>COLOR, NOT YET DEVELOPED OR DEVELOPED ALREADY.</p></pdiv>
<lb>
