UNCOLLECTED WORKS  [By Kaufman, B., 1925-1986] <attbytes>43Kb</attbytes><reflink></reflink><comcitn><TY>BOOK</TY><ID>Z200221539</ID><A1>Kaufman, Bob</A1><T1>Cranial Guitar: Selected Poems (1996)</T1><PBL>Coffee House Press</PBL><Y1>1981</Y1><T2>Literature Online</T2></comcitn></comhd2>
