<somhead><somauth>Kaufman, Bob<sombiog>1193</sombiog></somauth><mainhead>NOTES DIS&hyphen; AND RE&hyphen; GARDING ABOMUNISM</mainhead> <attbytes>3Kb</attbytes><volhead>Solitudes Crowded with Loneliness (1965)<publish>, New Directions</publish></volhead></somhead><reflink></reflink><comcitn><TY>DATA</TY><ID>Z300221648</ID><A1>Kaufman, Bob</A1><T1>NOTES DIS&hyphen; AND RE&hyphen; GARDING ABOMUNISM</T1><PBL>New Directions</PBL><Y1>1981</Y1><T2>Solitudes Crowded with Loneliness (1965)</T2><T3>Literature Online</T3></comcitn></comhd3>
<attribs><attpoet>Kaufman, Bob</attpoet><attidref>J3010128</attidref></attribs>
<newatts><attidref>J3010128</attidref><attdbase>Twentieth-Century American Poetry</attdbase><attdbase>Twentieth-Century African-American Poetry</attdbase><attpubl>New Directions</attpubl><atttitle><mainhead>NOTES DIS&hyphen; AND RE&hyphen; GARDING ABOMUNISM</mainhead><volhead>Solitudes Crowded with Loneliness (1965)<publish>, New Directions</publish></volhead></atttitle><attsize>3Kb</attsize><attperi>Twentieth-Century 1900-1999</attperi><attpubn1>1965</attpubn1><attpubn2>1965</attpubn2><attview></attview><attview></attview><attautid>1193</attautid></newatts>
<pdiv><firstl><l ln="1        ">Abomunism was founded by Barabbas, inspired by his dying</l></firstl>
<l ln="2        ">         words: &ldquo;I wanted to be in the middle, but I went too</l>
<l ln="3        ">         far out.&rdquo;</l>
<l ln="4        ">Abomunism's main function is to unite the soul with oatmeal</l>
<l ln="5        ">         cookies.</l>
<l ln="6        ">Abomunists love love, hate hate, drink drinks, smoke smokes,</l>
<l ln="7        ">         live lives, die deaths.</l>
<l ln="8        ">Abomunist writers write writing, or nothing at all.</l>
<l ln="9        ">Abomunist poetry, in order to be compleatly (Eng. sp.)</l>
<l ln="10      ">         understood, should be eaten ... except on fast days,</l>
<l ln="11      ">         slow days, and mornings of executions.</l>
<l ln="12      ">Abomunists, could they be a color, would be green,</l>
<l ln="13      ">         and tell everyone to go.</l>
<l ln="14      ">Uncrazy Abomunists crazy unAbomunists by proxy kicky</l>
<l ln="15      ">         tricks, as follows:</l>
<l ln="16      ">    By telling psychometric poets two heads are better</l>
<l ln="17      ">         than none.</l>
<l ln="18      ">    By selling middle names to impotent personnel</l>
<l ln="19      ">         managers.</l>
<l ln="20      ">    By giving children brightly wrapped candy fathers.</l>
<l ln="21      ">    By biting their own hands after feeding themselves.</l>
<l ln="22      ">    By calling taxis dirty names, while ordering fifths</l>
<l ln="23      ">         of milk.</l>
<l ln="24      ">    By walking across hills, ignoring up and down.</l>
<l ln="25      ">    By giving telescopes to peeping Toms.</l>
<l ln="26      ">    By using real names at false hotels.</l>
<pb n="79">
<l ln="27      ">Abomunists who feel their faith weakening will have to</l>
<l ln="28      ">         spend two weeks in Los Angeles.</l>
<l ln="29      ">When attacked, Abomunists think positive, repeating over</l>
<l ln="30      ">         and under: &ldquo;If I were a crime, I'd want to be</l>
<l ln="31      ">         committed ...</l>
<l ln="32      ">                       No! ... Wait!&rdquo;</l></pdiv></poem>
</div3>
